ui-layer / presentation layer
domain -> optional (for use cases)
data -> required (repo for business logics)
core -> utils, readme, (optional for ui components), di, navigation manager
app -> entrypoint, (recommended write to here di), navigation manager

ui-layer / presentation layer specification
each screen include:
1. screen (viewmodel)
2. viewmodel (repo, manager, service)
3. contract (events, state, messaging)
4. ui component (internal)


screen specification
1. viewmodel
2. event
3. content ->  HomeScreen / private HomeScreenContent
4. messaging

